gb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\'&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;淮海中路辟筑于1900年。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(36, 62, 133);&quot;&gt;辟筑之初，东段名西江路，西段名宝昌路，后又统称宝昌路。1915年更名为霞飞路；1943年更名泰山路，1945年，又宣布改称“林森中路”；1950年才改名为“淮海中路”。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=\'margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\'&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=\'margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\'&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;路名变换，伴随着业态变化。20世纪初，淮海中路只有一些小型洋货洋酒商铺。从20世纪20年代起，俄侨带动各国商人纷至沓来。到1935年前后，整条路的俄侨商店不下五六百家，还有数十家来自其它国家的商店企业。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=\'margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\'&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=\'margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\'&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/wm80Ec5NJpnuveVJECXNOt2Wic0mNYibl3VHeriahM7xZJxylIl9Zlagnt8nWyBmOl1XWic8ibnGIncAiaUibvApHse2g/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;amp;tp=webp&amp;amp;wxfrom=5&amp;amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;amp;wx_co=1&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: auto !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; border: 0px; top: 0px; left: 0px; right: 0px; bottom: 0px; width: 677px !important; visibility: visible !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=\'margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\'&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/wm80Ec5NJpnuveVJECXNOt2Wic0mNYibl3s58sbpRiahVdZh2Eq6kXficeiaEibaeWWPw3ygEO9tUSibrVpw0NT7PKRMg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;amp;tp=webp&amp;amp;wxfrom=5&amp;amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;amp;wx_co=1&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: auto !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; border: 0px; top: 0px; left: 0px; right: 0px; bottom: 0px; width: 677px !important; visibility: visible !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);&quot;&gt;20世纪30年代，俄侨在霞飞路（今淮海路）开设的照相图片馆和咖啡店&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=\'margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\'&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=\'margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\'&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;与此同时，华商在淮海路崛起。山东籍商人凭借通晓俄语、熟谙俄侨习性的优势，成为华商中的主力军。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(36, 62, 133);&quot;&gt;著名的福利面包公司就由山东籍商人创办，这就是今天的哈尔滨食品厂。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=\'margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\'&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=\'margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\'&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/wm80Ec5NJpnuveVJECXNOt2Wic0mNYibl3qUkraSLCrdsGFdlAKfBAFyB7erGnSIVKNCky4Gkr3UTjd2fBvPnO7Q/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;amp;tp=webp&amp;amp;wxfrom=5&amp;amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;amp;wx_co=1&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: auto !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; border: 0px; top: 0px; left: 0px; right: 0px; bottom: 0px; width: 677px !important; visibility: visible !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/wm80Ec5NJpnuveVJECXNOt2Wic0mNYibl3xUGb4E2sFZsjBP2c0pDJ67tsb7hqQ2yKZaeEsoA2iaRuvNj3FuBjpQQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;amp;tp=webp&amp;amp;wxfrom=5&amp;amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;amp;wx_co=1&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: auto !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; border: 0px; top: 0px; left: 0px; right: 0px; bottom: 0px; width: 677px !important; visibility: visible !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);&quot;&gt;由华商开设的福利面包店，就是今日的哈尔滨食品厂前身&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=\'margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\'&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=\'margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\'&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;受战乱影响，20世纪40年代的淮海路逐渐没落，不复旧日繁华。直至1950年起重获恢复和发展。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(36, 62, 133);&quot;&gt;1956年，全国最早、上海最大的妇女用品专业商店在淮海路开业。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;同年，淮海路网点大规模调整，进行了扩、并、撤、迁。调整中保留与发展了一些商店经营特色，如老大昌的西点、红房子的法式西菜。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n', null, '{\"audio\":\"\",\"video\":\"\",\"thumbnail\":\"portal\\/20181228\\/e7ca7f5e3b4f1f257e63ccf32b415759.jpg\",\"template\":\"\",\"photos\":[{\"url\":\"portal\\/20181228\\/e7ca7f5e3b4f1f257e63ccf32b415759.jpg\",\"name\":\"1122.jpg\"}]}');
INSERT INTO `cmf_portal_post` VALUES ('38', '0', '1', '1', '1', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '1545702912', '1545802771', '1545702780', '0', '杭州萧山国际机场商业', '', '萧山机场商业', '', 'default/20181226/f2362c9cb9ec02f6991f32b7034071db.png', '\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;杭州萧山国际机场&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;作为浙江省最大的空中门户，位于浙江省杭州市东部，距市中心&lt;/span&gt;27公里，是中国重要的干线机场、国际定期航班机场、对外开放的一类航空口岸和国际航班备降机场。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;杭州萧山国际机场通航以来，依托浙江省及周边地区充足的客货资源和旺盛的航空市场需求，运输生产迅猛增长，航线网络日趋规模。&lt;/span&gt;2007年机场旅客吞吐量首次突破千万人次大关，开始跻身世界繁忙机场行列。2014年旅客吞吐量达到2555万人次，增幅位居全国前十大机场第二位，其中国际(地区)年旅客吞吐量达到308万人次，目前是中国内地五大航空口岸、十大机场和世界百强机场之一。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:center;line-height:150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;default/20181226/f2362c9cb9ec02f6991f32b7034071db.png&quot; title=&quot;图片1.png&quot; alt=&quot;图片1.png&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;依托浙江丰富的旅游资源和长三角商务旅客资源优势，服务于&lt;/span&gt;“长三角”经济一体化进程，杭州萧山国际机场建立起布局清晰、层次合理、功能完善、主题明确的机场商业布局体系，将与未来建设的航空城融合互动。商业是机场的重大配套设施，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;上海誉圣&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;着力打造多元功能集聚、受众定位清晰的&lt;/span&gt;“机场购物中心”。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;杭州萧山国际机场立足于市场需求和西子古韵、空港文化、国际时尚融通互动的发展定位，致力于打造国际化、市场化、人性化、特色化、专业化的机场商业，构建引领国内、辐射长三角的机场商业平台。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:center;line-height:150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;default/20181226/ca887f45c2c3f61bffc75d7b261a892b.png&quot; title=&quot;图片2.png&quot; alt=&quot;图片2.png&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;目前，杭州萧山国际机场约&lt;/span&gt;160余家店铺。入驻的品牌有Burberry、Salvatore Ferragamo、Corneliani、Emporio Armani、Hugo Boss、Bally、CERRUTI1881、PORTS、Montblanc、王星记、星巴克、哈根达斯、肯德基、麦当劳、味千拉面、两岸咖啡等&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:center;line-height:150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px&quot;&gt; &lt;img src=&quot;default/20181226/f6c38db2795de1a6136e4afc3a3394b6.png&quot; title=&quot;图片3.png&quot; alt=&quot;图片3.png&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 32px; line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;未来的区域性航空枢纽不仅是一个停放飞机、旅客出入的机场，而是集乘机、购物、旅游、休闲、物流、会展等多功能于一体的&lt;/span&gt;“空港城”，满足旅客全方位、多方面的消费需求。机场商业将以消费需求为导向，以机场枢纽为载体，充分汲取城市商业开发亮点，打造购物公园、休闲空间、生活广场为特色的机场购物中心。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 32px; line-height: 150%; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;default/20181226/1ba94d0a9593290f00bf1b82d9ad1980.png&quot; title=&quot;图片4.png&quot; alt=&quot;图片4.png&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n', null, '{\"audio\":\"\",\"video\":\"\",\"thumbnail\":\"default\\/20181226\\/f2362c9cb9ec02f6991f32b7034071db.png\",\"template\":\"\"}');
INSERT INTO `cmf_portal_post` VALUES ('39', '0', '1', '1', '1', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '1545705745', '1545799935', '1545705660', '0', '上海浦东国际机场商业', '机场商业', '上海浦东机场商业', '', 'portal/20181225/aa416d9067893923506282a468476165.png', '\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 32px; text-align: justify; line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0px;&quot;&gt;上海浦东国际机场拥有&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0px;&quot;&gt;3万平方米的零售餐饮区域，包括国际顶级品牌、民族地域文化及特色美食等。在浦东机场的T1和T2航站楼、两航站楼之间的连廊都分布有商业餐饮，包括名品商业、民族商业、免税店、便利店、书店、药店，以及中西式餐饮、咖啡厅等各种商业业态，涵盖了众多一线品牌箱包、服饰、香水、化妆品、名表、珠宝首饰等。同时，还有体现上海特色的金山农民画，以及老城隍庙、冠生园等老字号商品。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 32px; line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;随着旅客对机场购物的认同度越来越高，商业对机场利润的贡献也在逐渐提升。据上海机场集团&lt;/span&gt;2011年的年报披露，2011年机场集团全年实现营业收入46.11亿元，其中商业餐饮租赁收入达到了12.36亿元，在营业收入中所占的比重为26.82%，为第二大收入来源。而2000年，机场集团的该项收入为10.02亿元，在全年营业收入中的比重为23.94%。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 32px; line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;随着旅客吞吐量逐步增长，聚集了众多国际航线的枢纽机场商业开发优势越来越明显。有经常出国的旅客介绍，不少国外机场的餐饮价格与市区不相上下，很多机场把交通枢纽与购物消费空间结合得很好，使机场成为一个大多数人能接受的购物中心。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 32px; line-height: 150%; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;portal/20181225/aa416d9067893923506282a468476165.png&quot; title=&quot;图片1.png&quot; alt=&quot;图片1.png&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n', null, '{\"audio\":\"\",\"video\":\"\",\"thumbnail\":\"portal\\/20181225\\/aa416d9067893923506282a468476165.png\",\"template\":\"\"}');
